  <p><strong>GATHERING</strong></p>
  <p>I've got some good news and some absolutely unbelievably incredible news for you. First off, the dates for this year's Gathering have been set (Yay!!!), they are the 25th to the 27th September 2009. Secondly, and here comes the bestestest bit........IT'S GONNA BE IN NELSON! TA DA!!! Told you it was good. :)</p>
  <p> We're holding it at Bridge Valley Adventure Centre. More details will follow in the coming weeks, but for now, I need you to start thinking about if you'll be there or not (pretty silly question really cos who wouldn't want to come to Nelson). Please can you get back to me ASAP on whether you'll be there and numbers-wise on family members accompanying too.</p>
  <p>      Costings for the food and accomodation part of the weekend are below. We'll need to decide as a community (funny how that word keeps cropping up in Incedo messages lately) as to whether we go for the standard or deluxe catering options. So maybe on your rsvp, indicate which you're up for and if there's a large consensus towards deluxe (highly unlikely cos we're all broke youth workers) then we'll head in that direction. If it's half and half or leaning towards standard then we'll go with standard. The food there is really good, whatever option we go for, so don't think that standard means bread, water and peas as a staple diet for the weekend. Deluxe just means extra extra yum yum. </p>
  <p> Any questions give me a call, email, carrier pigeon messgage or telepathic thought. Sorry, I can't accept semaphore anymore. </p>
  <p> Cheers</p>
